==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dement
<hw>De*ment"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dementare</ets>, fr. <ets>demens</ets>, <ets>-mentis</ets>, out of
one's mind, mad; <ets>de</ets> + <ets>mens</ets> mind. See
<er>Mental</er>, and cf. <er>Dementate</er>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of
reason; to make mad.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Bale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dement</ent>⟦br⟧

